      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, it's mostly gone now so i'm thinking i just need to drink some water and sleep it off. it's probably just stress from finals or something, right? and i'm feeling a bit nauseous too, maybe i just ate something weird. do you think i should just take some ibuprofen and wait until morning?",
